[h3 
	" About This Run
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" This run is TAS of Old axe armor Version which is in special mode of Castlevania - Portrait of Ruin.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Appears when you kill and clear 1000 enemy old axe armor in Jonathan mode. So you need a DSM for SRAM generation.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" SRAM
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Created based on the latest version of All Bosses TAS. DSM is here.
	$LF
	"-> http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/get/511747355/mtbRc-CVPoR-OldAxeArmerMode%20Velifiler%20V3.dsm
	$LF
	"This dsm was created using DeSmuME-0.9.9
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Tricks
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Most the tricks and glitches used in this run can be found here: http://tasvideos.org/2255S.html and http://tasvideos.org/3657S
	$LF
	"Roughly different from Richter Mode in the following points.
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Character change can't be used
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Multiple hits can't be used
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" There are fewer means of enemy avoidance
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" There are few means of HP recovery
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	" Method to avoid the enemy
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Invulnerability use by Takes Damage
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Kill the enemy
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Invulnerability use of smash
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"If you hit smash, it will go backwards, but if you use it again at the moment you hit it, you can avoid going backwards.
	$LF
	"Puppet Master is very slow and not used.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" HP recovery
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"In the following two places in consideration of efficiency
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" HP MAX UP at the entrance of Master's Keep
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Central savepoint of Burnt Paradice
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"HP MAX UP is acquired using motion cancellation.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Motion cancellation
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"The level up and MAX UP treasure chest motion can be canceled by activating Puppet Master at the same time.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Puppet Master Zipping
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Release the Puppet Master while hitting the wall with a thin ceiling. Then this Puppet Master comes through the wall. This TAS uses only one part of Entrance.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Moving method
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Back dash cancellation loop seems to be the fastest
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"forward -> backdash,forward+crouch,...
	$LF
	"8192-> (15832+13432)/2=14632
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Route
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Basically it is the same as Richter. But I replace Nation of Fools and Sandy Grave with Richter Mode. This is because I thought that this was earlier as a result of considering the balance with MP.
	$LF
]p
